channel.title: Connecting Error, out of my league
channel.description:
Well, I had server running buetifully, then, all of a sudden today, everything seems to go haywire, and noone can connect, and I tried Hamachi, and made a network, but yet, noone can connect! I've tried forwarding my port through the firewall. It's out of my league, I got nothing when it comes to IP's :( If anyone can help me, you must be a genious. This is out of my league! And, my ip on Hamachi is different to the one on www.whatismyip.com
Please, someone help
